{"tid":2342541,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"土木工程師前途佳 重視溝通及解難","createTime":"2020-12-27T08:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T08:05:46.000Z","uid":225931,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ca55daf311ad31a9d0f4d17aa572748ca7778eee","tid":2342541,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"土木工程師全權負責土木工程各項設施的規劃與設計、及工程施工現場監造與管理等，承擔工程成敗的責任，是工程建造過程中的靈魂人物。<br />\n<br />\n土木工程師前景<br />\n土木工程涉及的範圍非常廣泛，基本上可分為兩類建設：基建項目及樓宇建設。<br />\n<br />\n基建包括橋梁、水壩、道路、斜坡鞏固等；而樓宇建設則包括高樓大廈等。香港近年有多個基建項目，亦有市區重建、舊樓維修等項目，因此需要的人才亦大增，對土木工程界尤為有利。<br />\n<br />\n在香港，土木工程師是專業人士，畢業生起薪介乎1.8至2萬港元，收入可觀，前景不俗。"},{"pid":"28746ec75d6bd54cf8c3b6202d61cb1daf82aea1","tid":2342541,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:15:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.beagazine.com.hk/recommendation/%E5%9C%9F%E6%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%89%8D%E9%80%94%E4%BD%B3-%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%96%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%A3%E9%9B%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beagazine.com.hk%2Frecommendation%2F%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%259C%25A8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2580%2594%25E4%25BD%25B3-%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%25BA%259D%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%259B%25A3%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=bec677cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.beagazine.com.hk/recommendation/%E5%9C%9F%E6%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%89%8D%E9%80%94%E4%BD%B3-%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%96%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%A3%E9%9B%A3/</a>"},{"pid":"43d1c171e1e92a13032fc7da3be8a24fdef704fd","tid":2342541,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"唔講下個structural 嗰啲有牌都係得20幾K?"},{"pid":"e4da2cb1c79b442c90aa3e8452b2fcfaf2f6f321","tid":2342541,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}